name: SP3 (Paulista x Pamplona)
description: From a series of pictures of places along Avenida Paulista, São Paulo's main commerce strip. Taken 20 April 2012. The bizarre pyramidal building is headquarters to FIESP,  the local manufacturers' association, which serves as an influential mouthpiece for the views and demands of business owners in general, tied to the political right wing. Originally released as HeN OBJKT 19889 on 1 April 2021. Upsampled, denoised and newly color graded for this re-release.
